    passage: "POSITION VACANT: WAREHOUSE SUPERVISOR\nEverest Freight Solutions | Christchurch, New Zealand\n\nEverest Freight Solutions is a leading third-party logistics provider operating across New Zealand and Australia. We are seeking an experienced Warehouse Supervisor to lead day-to-day operations at our Christchurch distribution facility.\n\nKEY DUTIES:\n• Supervise a team of 20 warehouse staff across inbound and outbound operations\n• Monitor and report on daily KPIs including pick accuracy, dispatch rates, and labour productivity\n• Conduct safety inspections and ensure compliance with Health & Safety regulations\n• Liaise with transport carriers regarding scheduling and exceptions\n• Train and mentor new team members\n\nREQUIREMENTS:\n• Minimum 3 years' experience in a warehouse supervisory role\n• Current forklift licence (counterbalance)\n• Strong working knowledge of WMS software\n• Excellent communication and team leadership skills\n• NZ Certificate in Logistics (Level 4) desirable but not required\n\nSalary: NZD 68,000–75,000 | Applications close: August 16\nApply: recruitment@everestfreight.co.nz",
