    passage: "SUNRIDGE GARDEN CENTRE\nSpring Sale Event — This Weekend Only!\n\nSunridge Garden Centre is excited to announce our biggest spring sale of the year, running this Saturday and Sunday from 8:00 a.m. to 5:00 p.m.\n\nHIGHLIGHTS:\n• Up to 40% off all native plants and seedlings\n• 25% off all garden tools and equipment\n• Buy 2, get 1 free on all potting mix and mulch bags\n• Free expert advice sessions with our horticulturalists, running every hour from 9:00 a.m.\n\nThis sale is in-store only and cannot be combined with any other offer or loyalty discount. Gift cards are accepted but cannot be used to purchase sale items at a further reduced price.\n\nSunridge Garden Centre is located at 14 Bloomfield Road, Sunridge Hills. Free parking is available on site.\n\nCall ahead to confirm stock availability on specific items: (02) 9445 6700\n\nSee you in the garden!",
