    passage: "HAWTHORNE ACADEMY\nGraduate Programme — Expression of Interest\n\nHawthorne Academy invites applications from recent graduates for its highly competitive two-year Graduate Programme, commencing February next year.\n\nThe programme offers rotations across four core business units — Finance, Strategy, Operations, and Client Services — providing participants with broad exposure to the firm's functions and senior leadership.\n\nPROGRAMME HIGHLIGHTS:\n• Structured rotations every six months\n• Dedicated mentor from the senior leadership team\n• Three formal training blocks per year (including one international module in Singapore)\n• Competitive salary of AUD 72,000 in Year 1, increasing to AUD 80,000 in Year 2\n• Permanent placement consideration upon successful completion\n\nELIGIBILITY:\nApplicants must have completed an undergraduate or postgraduate degree within the last two years and achieved a minimum GPA of 3.0 (or equivalent).\n\nApplications open August 1 and close September 15.\nApply at hawthorneacademy.com.au/graduates",
