    passage: "[Document 1 – Training Programme Brochure]\n\nPROFESSIONAL DEVELOPMENT SERIES\nApex Business Institute\n\nCourse: Advanced Negotiation Skills for Business Professionals\nFormat: 3-day intensive (in-person)\nDates available: April 22–24 | May 20–22 | June 17–19\nVenue: Apex Business Institute, Level 6, 88 George Street\nFee: AUD 2,100 per participant (includes materials, meals, and certificate)\nGroup discount: 15% for 3 or more participants from the same organisation\n\nThis course is suitable for managers, senior executives, and professionals whose roles involve contract negotiation, supplier management, or business development.\n\nTopics covered:\n• Interest-based negotiation frameworks\n• Managing cross-cultural negotiations\n• Dealing with difficult counterparts\n• Structuring and closing complex deals\n\nCPD points: 18 points upon completion\n\n[Document 2 – Registration Enquiry]\n\nFrom: Marcus Thornton <m.thornton@vertexgroup.com.au>\nTo: pd@apexbi.com.au\nDate: March 28\n\nDear Apex Team,\n\nI would like to register four participants from Vertex Group for the Advanced Negotiation Skills course. We prefer the May 20–22 dates.\n\nCould you confirm the group discount applies to our booking of four people, and what the total cost would be?\n\nAlso, one of our participants has a dietary requirement (gluten-free). Could you confirm meals can be accommodated?\n\nThank you,\nMarcus Thornton\n\n[Document 3 – Booking Confirmation]\n\nFrom: Apex Business Institute <pd@apexbi.com.au>\nTo: Marcus Thornton <m.thornton@vertexgroup.com.au>\nDate: March 30\n\nDear Mr. Thornton,\n\nThank you for your registration enquiry.\n\nWe can confirm the following:\n\n1. Group discount: The 15% group discount applies to groups of 3 or more, so your booking of 4 participants qualifies. The per-person fee is AUD 1,785 (AUD 2,100 × 0.85). Total for 4 participants: AUD 7,140.\n\n2. Dietary requirements: We can absolutely accommodate a gluten-free meal option. Please provide the participant's full name when completing the registration form so our catering team can make the necessary arrangements.\n\n3. Places on May 20–22 are available but filling quickly. We recommend confirming your booking by April 4 to secure your spots.\n\nPlease visit apexbi.com.au/register to complete the booking.\n\nApex Business Institute",
